zeExternalLibraryDynamicAccess --coordinates=group:artifact:version\\n```\\n\\nThis resolves the requested library, runs Native Image with `Preserve` and `TrackDynamicAccess`, and prints a JSON summary suitable for issue comments.\\n\\n### Generating Metadata\\n\\nGenerates metadata for a single library coordinate. If `agentAllowedPackages` is provided, a new user-code-filter.json will be created or updated from those packages or from package roots derived from the resolved library JAR.\\n\\n- `coordinates`: group:artifact:version (single coordinate only)\\n- `agentAllowedPackages`: comma-separated package list, `fromJar`, or `-` for none\\n\\nExamples:\\n   ```console\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3 --agentAllowedPackages=fromJar\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3 --agentAllowedPackages=org.example.app,com.acme.service\\n\\n[93 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777427452750}]}\n382:  tests/src/org.jline/jline-terminal/3.19.0/.gitignore\n433:  tests/src/org.jline/jline-terminal/3.19.0/.gitignore\n489:  tests/src/org.jline/jline-terminal/3.19.0/.gitignore\n514:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_start\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_SLOzaIxdFmQ2Wl448lcWilQP|fc_034d25b9c522b1ea0169f163ffcc3081a29898e0cc7e62cdc3\", \"toolName\": \"bash\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"tests/src/org.jline/jline-terminal/3.19.0/build.gradle\\ntests/src/org.jline/jline-terminal/3.19.0/build/jacoco/test.exec\\ntests/src/org.jline/jline-terminal/3.19.0/build/libs/org.jline.jline-terminal_tests.jar\\ntests/src/org.jline/jline-terminal/3.19.0/build/native/generated/generateTestResourcesConfigFile/resource-config.json\\ntests/src/org.jline/jline-terminal/3.19.0/build/native/nativeTestCompile/dynamic-access/jline-terminal-3.19.0/r